h, i am going to kill it.  If i see a 51+ mage in the zone, i will more than likely offer to MQ with that mage unless they have been a complete ass to me or someone i know.<br><br>Failing that, i would probably take the cloak and MQ it with any good mage friends i have that are the level to do the quest.<br><br>You repeat that level doesnt matter... well it does.  Its awefully funny for you to whine about a level 26 monk wanting to kill quillmane, while you are 16 levels from even being able to ZONE INTO some of the zones you will need to do the quest.. let alone actually contribute.<br><br>There is ZERO wrong with you wanting to start early.  You would be surprised.. most of the mages that get this item get it through MQ ing with a friend who happend to pass by and kill it.<br><br>If you manage to kill it, fine, great in fact, however, if i am passing through the zone and saw it up, and also saw some level 30 person whining ( yes whining ) about their epic i wouldnt think a second thought about killing it if it were un engaged.<br><br>Like someone else said,  if you are concentrating on your epic at level 30, you really need to examine why you are actually playing this game , or you need to get some much higher level friends to basically twink your epic for you.<br><br> <p><a href="http://www.mithrilweb.com//"target="web"><img src="http://www.mithrilweb.com/images/sigs/llosig.jpg" border="0"></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#E5E5E6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/usuzannadreamingheart.showPublicProfile?language=EN>SuzannaDreamingheart</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>w4nn4b3!</span><br> <font color=#000033>(2/12/02 4:21:40 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumrantsandravesbalancingissues.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1695.topic&index=14>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Mage Nuke</span><hr size=1> I am a