ou wanted to rant. Well, you will get rants back. <br><br>People who expect epics to be handed to them at 50 or even 46 annoy the hell out of me. But at level 30 ... good god.<br><br>If you can kill Quillmane, and get your cloak, good for you. But there is no way in hell I'd default to you if I killed it before you, based on it being part of the Mage epic, with you at level 30. I'd give (not sell) it to a Mage who can actually use it. I know several who are stuck on Quillmane, who actually might complete their epics in the next few weeks if they get it. Come back in 16 levels time, and I'd give you a different answer. Until then, live with it.<br><br>And Tardaan is not the one looking greedy here. You are.<br> <p>--------------------------------------<BR><BR><A HREF="http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=56579">Suzanna Dreamingheart</A><BR>Mighty Mage! of 59 Seasons<BR><A HREF="http://pub36.ezboard.com/bheroes795">Heroes of the Old Lands</A><BR>Lanys T'Vyl.<BR><A HREF="http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Action=Journal&Id=56579">[Journal]</A> <A HREF="http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Action=Journal&Jid=11608&Id=56579">[Epic Quest Progress]</A></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#D5D4D5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ujellah.showPublicProfile?language=EN>jellah</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>h0x0r!</span><br> <font color=#000033>(2/12/02 4:32:57 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumrantsandravesbalancingissues.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1695.topic&index=15>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Mage Nuke</span><hr size=1> Just to add this, dont make too many assumptions when someone kills Quill based on their class or level. My husbands rogue happend to be around and it popped, he killed cause<br><br>FIRST... he can use it<br><br>SECOND... a good f